---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout>
    <main class="app-container pt-36">
        <h1 class="text-6xl pb-2 font-bold">About Us</h1>
    </main>
    <section class="app-container py-12 mb-8">
        <div
                class="prose prose-neutral prose-lg md:prose-xl dark:prose-invert prose-img:rounded-xl prose-figure:text-center prose-img:mx-auto"
        >
            <p>
                Welcome to China Expat & Travel Guide, your everyday resource for living, working, and exploring life in China.
                Our mission is to provide clear, practical, and reliable guides that help expats adapt to life in China
                with confidence.
            </p>
            <p>
                From navigating local food, finding housing, understanding transportation, to exploring travel
                opportunities and experiencing Chinese culture, our guides cover all aspects of daily life. Each article
                is designed to be concise, actionable, and easy to follow, making your transition to life in China
                smoother and more enjoyable.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you are moving to China for work, study, or adventure, China Expat & Travel Guide is here to make your
                everyday life simpler, more informed, and truly enjoyable.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our Goal:
            </p>
            <p>
                To empower expats with practical knowledge and tips, helping you live comfortably and confidently in
                China.
            </p>
            <p>
                Keywords naturally included: China Expat & Travel Guide, living in China, expat life in China, China lifestyle,
                moving to China.
            </p>

        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
